To revert the changes and restore the system to its previous state (which relies on the CDN for styling, causing the "blinking" FOUC but ensuring the design renders correctly without a complex local build), I will add the **Tailwind CSS CDN** and the **Custom Theme Configuration** back into `index.html`.

I will also clean up `index.css` to remove the local build directives, ensuring there are no conflicts.

# Updated files:

## index.html

Restoring Tailwind CSS CDN, Theme Configuration, and inline styles to revert to the CDN-based architecture.

