To guarantee that receipts, invoices, and waybills print cleanly without any overlays or website UI elements (like modals or backdrops) appearing in the background, I am updating `index.css`.

The key is to enforce a very specific `@media print` block that:
1.  Sets `body` visibility to `hidden` (hiding the entire app).
2.  Forces the `print-force-container` (which wraps the invoice) to be `visible` and positioned at `top: 0; left: 0`.
3.  Explicitly hides any potential modal backdrops (e.g., elements with `bg-black/50` or `modal-backdrop` classes) using `display: none !important`.

I will now apply these rigorous CSS rules.

# Updated files:

## index.css

Update print styles to aggressively hide all overlays, modals, and backdrops, ensuring only the invoice container is visible on a clean white page.

```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

/* Custom Base Styles */
body { 
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}

h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 { 
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; 
}

/* Custom Utilities */
@layer utilities {
  .scrollbar-hide::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
  }
  .scrollbar-hide {
      -ms-overflow-style: none;
      scrollbar-width: none;
  }

  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slideUp 0.4s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-scale-up {
    animation: scaleUp 0.3s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-slide-right {
    animation: slideRight 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-pulse-once {
    animation: pulseOnce 0.5s ease-in-out;
  }
}

/* Keyframes */
@keyframes slideUp {
  0% { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
  100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes scaleUp {
  0% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0; }
  100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  0% { opacity: 0; }
  100% { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes slideRight {
  0% { transform: translateX(100%); }
  100% { transform: translateX(0); }
}

@keyframes pulseOnce {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
}

/* --- ROBUST PRINT STYLES --- */
@media print {
  /* 1. Reset Body: Force white background and auto sizing */
  body {
    background: white !important;
    height: auto !important;
    width: 100% !important;
    overflow: visible !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
  }

  /* 2. Hide Everything Else by default */
  body * {
    visibility: hidden;
  }

  /* 3. Force The Print Container to Show */
  .print-force-container {
    visibility: visible !important;
    position: absolute !important;
    top: 0 !important;
    left: 0 !important;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: auto !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    background: white !important;
    z-index: 99999 !important; /* Maximum Z-Index */
    display: block !important;
  }

  /* 4. Show Children of Print Container */
  .print-force-container * {
    visibility: visible !important;
  }

  /* 5. Explicitly Hide Trouble Elements (Modals, Backdrops, Navs) */
  #root, 
  nav, 
  header, 
  footer, 
  .fixed, 
  .absolute.inset-0, /* Typical modal backdrop class */
  .modal-backdrop, 
  [role="dialog"],
  .bg-black\/80, 
  .bg-black\/60,
  .bg-black\/50 {
    display: none !important;
  }

  /* 6. Ensure Graphics Print Correctly */
  body {
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }

  /* 7. Reset Page Margins to allow full width printing if needed */
  @page {
    margin: 0.5cm;
    size: auto;
  }
}

